data.title: Air Force News Jan-Jun 1941
data.meta_description: Air Force News ~ Jan-Jun 1941 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf) or read book online for free. The document discusses several changes and expansions to US Air Corps units and bases in early 1941. New squadrons are being activated at Lowry Field in Colorado, and existing squadrons are being reorganized into four groups. Construction is nearly complete on new barracks and facilities at Hamilton Field in California to accommodate 15,000 personnel. The Cal-Aero Academy flight school in Ontario, California is expanding to triple its original size.
